The paper proposes a system that uses deep learning and machine learning approaches for melanoma recognition in dermoscopy images. This involves image segmentation and analysis, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the evaluation of the system using a benchmark dataset, which could fall under information retrieval (cs.IR) or multimedia (cs.MM).
